  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help kids to overcome educational lag due to COVID</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The pandemic is causing gaps in learning, increasing school dropouts and inequality, which will affect children into adulthood. The situation in rural communities, is even more devastating since families don&apos;t have internet access to continue children&apos;s education and parents have lost income. This project aims to overcome the educational lag and keep children interested in learning, in outdoor and sanitized space, where they can freely explore and discover; share and learn with proper guidance.</narrative>
  </description>
